{"tid":2250072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人發現香港主流媒體/正苦 每日強調幾多人中 但幾多人死幾多人無事康復只係約略帶過 其至唔敢提","createTime":"2020-10-20T00:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T00:22:51.000Z","uid":78016,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6383c27768893e766b07c204db5f104078d6ff44","tid":2250072,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:17:22.000Z","msg":"香港廢炎死亡數字唔見得人<br />\n大半年先瓜100個廢老<br />\nTvb 日日播外國幾多人死於廢炎 (因為撞車死 Cancer 死都計廢炎殺)<br />\n隻字都唔敢提/輕輕帶過香港廢老死亡人數 (香港無得claim 錢 唔洗做大數)<br />\n康復數字完全無聽過<br />\n更加唔洗講肺無花/跳高過1cm/完全無事康復有幾多人<br />\n沸水都黎到了各位連囝恐懼撚發覺自己被人控制接收咩資訊未<br />\n勇仔都露出左真面目啦 裝睡嘅人真係永遠唔會醒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa24fc515509702a2d7a6d49f5c03133282add","tid":2250072,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbba9fe24539d28728c52c8c7033e627229ea1b6","tid":2250072,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557f56abd7acfdb047a369522aba26be63534b45","tid":2250072,"uid":344679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"Just a flu"},{"pid":"baa2efc92d18855b5b2bc7cb82f3c336d83a17fb","tid":2250072,"uid":259842,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:48:26.000Z","msg":"2018年冬季流感都死左3百幾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/04/20180404/20180404_173413_427.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2018%2F04%2F20180404%2F20180404_173413_427.html&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=b1a598f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/04/20180404/20180404_173413_427.html</a>"}